      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static Class[] STANDARD_CONSTRUCTOR_SIG
      Unless a custom RuntimeModelDescriptorFactory is used, it is expected that implementations of MappedSuperclassDescriptor define a constructor accepting the following arguments: * MappedSuperclassMapping is the boot-model description of the mapped-superclass * IdentifiableTypeDescriptor is the runtime-model descriptor of mapped-superclass's super type * RuntimeModelCreationContext - access to additional information useful while constructing the descriptor.
